  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/29/things-to-know-about-how-julian-assange-and-us-prosecutors-arrived-at-a-plea-deal-to-end-his-case.webp" alt="Things to know about how Julian Assange and US prosecutors arrived at a plea deal to end his case"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Things to know about how Julian Assange and US prosecutors arrived at a plea deal to end his case</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The plea deal resulting in WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange's freedom was the culmination of a lengthy negotiation process that accelerated in recent months and featured numerous proposals and counterproposals.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/29/things-to-know-about-how-julian-assange-and-us-prosecutors-arrived-at-a-plea-deal-to-end-his-case/"  >(Eric Tucker, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 22:49:48 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 22:49:48 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="MARK SHERMAN, Associated Press, KLAS, CBS News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/us/2024/06/28/supreme-court-makes-it-harder-to-charge-capitol-riot-defendants-with-obstruction-charge-trump-faces.webp" alt="Supreme Court makes it harder to charge Capitol riot defendants with obstruction, charge Trump faces"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Supreme Court makes it harder to charge Capitol riot defendants with obstruction, charge Trump faces</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WASHINGTON (AP) — The Supreme Court on Friday limited a federal obstruction law that has been used to charge hundreds of Capitol riot defendants as well as former President Donald Trump.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/28/supreme-court-makes-it-harder-to-charge-capitol-riot-defendants-with-obstruction-charge-trump-faces/"  >(MARK SHERMAN, Associated Press, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
