           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Former Uvalde school police chief and officer indicted over Robb Elementary response, reports say</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The indictments were kept under seal until the men were in custody, and both were expected to turn themselves in by Friday, news outlets reported.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/06/27/former-uvalde-school-police-chief-and-officer-indicted-over-robb-elementary-response-reports-say/"  >(JIM VERTUNO, Associated Press, WGN 9)</a>
