    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trial for Lindsay Shiver, accused in plot to kill husband, delayed</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Police said Lindsay and Robert Shiver were in the middle of a bitter divorce when she allegedly asked two men to kill him.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/28/lindsay-shiver-trial-delayed-accused-plot-kill-husband/"  >(Rob Hess, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
