           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Ultra-Orthodox Jews protest Israel's military service ruling</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      BNEI BRAK, Israel (AP) — Hundreds of ultra-Orthodox Jewish men blocked a major highway in central Israel for two hours on Thursday to protest a recent Supreme Court decision ordering young religious men to enlist for military service.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/06/28/ultra-orthodox-jews-block-highway-to-protest-israels-new-mandatory-military-service-ruling/"  >(AMI BENTOV, Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 20:48:57 +0000">
