           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">The perils of overengineering generative AI systems</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Cloud is the easiest way to build generative AI systems; that’s why cloud revenues are skyrocketing. However, many of these systems are overengineered, which drives complexity and unnecessary costs. Overengineering is a familiar issue.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/28/the-perils-of-overengineering-generative-ai-systems/"  >(Info World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 24 Jun 2024 23:17:15 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 24 Jun 2024 23:17:15 +0000">
