           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Why NASA astronauts are delayed at the space station after Boeing Starliner launch</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Two astronauts are spending extra time at the International Space Station as NASA and Boeing troubleshoot capsule problems that popped up on the way there.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/26/why-nasa-astronauts-are-delayed-at-the-space-station-after-boeing-starliner-launch/"  >(Stephanie Nano, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
