           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">YouTube fuels the AI machine&#8212;including your family reunion</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The promised artificial intelligence revolution requires data. Lots and lots of data. OpenAI and Google have begun using YouTube videos to train their text-based AI models.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/29/youtube-openai-google-ai-machine-models-training-family-reunion/"  >(The Conversation, Fast Company)</a>
    </p>
