    <h3 itemprop="headline">Amazon is reviewing whether Perplexity AI improperly scraped online content</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Amazon is reviewing claims that the artificial intelligence startup Perplexity AI is scraping content — including from prominent news sites — without approval.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/06/28/amazon-is-reviewing-whether-perplexity-ai-improperly-scraped-online-content/"  >(HALELUYA HADERO, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
