    <h3 itemprop="headline">NBA Draft: Two CU Buffaloes are selected, Nuggets grab big man</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The NBA Draft's first round is in the books as not one but two Colorado Buffaloes heard their names called tonight.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/27/nba-draft-two-cu-buffaloes-are-selected-nuggets-grab-big-man/"  >(Big Will Levenson, KREX 5)</a>
