           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Bronny James, the son of LeBron James, drafted by Lakers</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      It was the dream that LeBron James first floated a few years ago, the notion of playing in the NBA alongside one of his sons. And it's a step closer to reality now.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/27/bronny-james-the-son-of-lebron-james-drafted-by-lakers/"  >(Associated Press, PIX 11)</a>
