           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">NBA draft: When will Bronny James get picked?</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The son of career scoring leader LeBron James was not selected in the first round Wednesday in the NBA draft, and now will wait to see if he's picked in the second round when selections resume Thursday afternoon.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/27/nba-draft-when-will-bronny-james-get-picked/"  >(The Associated Press, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
