    <h3 itemprop="headline">Canadian Olympic basketball GM: Warriors blocking Wiggins from playing in Paris</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Canadian Olympic basketball team general manager Rowan Barrett said Friday that Golden State is blocking Andrew Wiggins from competing in Paris, while the Warriors countered it was a mutual decision between the team and Wiggins.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/06/29/canadian-olympic-basketball-gm-warriors-blocking-wiggins-from-playing-in-paris/"  >(Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
