           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Will they curse? How many 'non-facts'? Betting sites offer Biden-Trump debate wagers</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Online sportsbooks are betting big on this week's highly anticipated debate between President Biden and former President Trump, offering wagers on everything from the candidates' sartorial choices to whether there will be long pauses or profanity.  One site, BetOnline.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/25/will-they-curse-how-many-non-facts-betting-sites-offer-biden-trump-debate-wagers/"  >(Judy Kurtz, PIX 11)</a>
    </p>
