           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Connecticut Gov. Ned Lamont tests positive for COVID-19</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      HARTFORD, Conn. (PIX11) -- Connecticut Gov. Ned Lamont has tested positive for COVID-19, a spokesperson said Thursday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/27/connecticut-gov-ned-lamont-tests-positive-for-covid-19/"  >(Finn Hoogensen, PIX 11)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
