      <img src="/static8/politics/2024/06/28/heres-why-it-would-be-tough-for-democrats-to-replace-joe-biden-on-the-presidential-ticket.webp" alt="Here's why it would be tough for Democrats to replace Joe Biden on the presidential ticket"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Here's why it would be tough for Democrats to replace Joe Biden on the presidential ticket</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WASHINGTON (AP) — President Joe Biden's halting debate performance has led some in his own party to begin questioning whether he should be replaced on the ballot before November. There is no evidence Biden is willing to end his campaign.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/28/heres-why-it-would-be-tough-for-democrats-to-replace-joe-biden-on-the-presidential-ticket/"  >(WILL WEISSERT, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 04:48:49 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 04:48:49 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Brett Samuels, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/politics/2024/06/28/biden-says-we-did-well-no-concerns-about-debate-performance.webp" alt="Biden says 'we did well,' no concerns about debate performance"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Biden says 'we did well,' no concerns about debate performance</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Biden brushed off concerns about his debate performance against former President Trump Thursday despite widespread panic among Democrats about how the night played out.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/28/biden-says-we-did-well-no-concerns-about-debate-performance/"  >(Brett Samuels, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 19:21:38 -0400">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 19:21:38 -0400">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
