    <h3 itemprop="headline">WATCH: Dem. Rep. snatches phone in testy airport exchange over Biden's mental clarity: 'Who owns you?'</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Democratic Rep. Marcy Kaptur got into a contentious exchange with a man at a Detroit airport who asked her about President Biden&apos;s cognitive abilities after Thursday&apos;s debate.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/28/watch-dem-rep-snatches-phone-in-testy-airport-exchange-over-bidens-mental-clarity-who-owns-you/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div></div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 18:50:17 +0000">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 28 Jun 2024 18:50:17 +0000">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="LINDSAY WHITEHURST, Associated Press, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static8/politics/2024/06/28/supreme-court-rejects-trump-ally-steve-bannons-bid-to-delay-prison-sentence.webp" alt="Supreme Court rejects Trump ally Steve Bannon&#8217;s bid to delay prison sentence"
           itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
           referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Supreme Court rejects Trump ally Steve Bannon&#8217;s bid to delay prison sentence</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WASHINGTON (AP) — The Supreme Court on Friday rejected a bid to delay a prison sentence for longtime Trump ally Steve Bannon as he appeals his conviction for defying a subpoena in the congressional investigation into the U.S. Capitol insurrection.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/06/28/supreme-court-rejects-trump-ally-steve-bannons-bid-to-delay-prison-sentence/"  >(LINDSAY WHITEHURST, Associated Press, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
